{
  "doc_id": "18689",
  "text": "Cases 1-4 received oral folinic acid at a dose of 1 mg/kg/ day, and cases 6 and 8 received higher doses (3 mg/kg/ day, Table 2 ). The doses of folinic acid were selected according to previous reported protocols for the treatment of profound cerebral folate deficiencies [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Lumbar punctures following therapy were performed in three patients (cases 1, 2 and 8; Table 2 ). The remaining cases declined undergoing lumbar puncture.",
